{"tid":551155,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 將會為 Android 手機加入電話通話錄音功能","createTime":"2018-02-05T11:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T08:13:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5393ba528fafc28a121f18b50d0fdb26e2e688a1","tid":551155,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:31:33.000Z","msg":"Google 在 Android 開放原始碼項目（ASOP）中加入通話錄音功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，代表此項功能有望成為 Android 系統的預設功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用家可以 1400Hz 頻率進行錄音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。為了讓通話雙方都知道對話被錄音，系統每隔 15 秒就會播出通知音效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，現階段尚未知道保存好的錄音會儲存在哪個位置，以及能否進行雲端保存。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn-unwire-hk.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1-%E5%8E%BB%E6%B0%B4%E5%8D%B0-1200x675.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-unwire-hk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F1-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%258D%25B0-1200x675.png&h=09a17bb5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/02/05/android-p-phone-recording/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2Fandroid-p-phone-recording%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=n4WfTD7JfggnSmlMA93jA%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=4bc161c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/02/05/android-p-phone-recording/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"46e5d3e5a23522872ad88001e1fb8e90cc143fe8","tid":551155,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:32:02.000Z","msg":"這項功能並非首次在 Android 上登場，早前 Google 曾與 Samsung 、小米等手機製作商合作，在特定機型上提供這個功能，方便用家保留電話通話的內容，但通話錄音功能的 API 一直未有列為標準項目。早在 2006 年， LG 已推出一部主打通話錄音功能的手機，顯示這個功能一直以來都存在都一定需求。"},{"pid":"56b5a54aa12a52cfa32d9e5dc10c015130bb8937","tid":551155,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:32:27.000Z","msg":"雖然 ASOP 加入了通話錄音功能的項目，代表會成為 Android 系統的原生功能，但全球有部份地區以私隱權為由，禁止手機生產商提供此類功能，相信仍會根據各地的規範開放提供。"},{"pid":"43859c707ac0d63d7938dd01728d7c6b5366e648","tid":551155,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"另有消息指 Google 將會進一步加強對開發者和廠商的限制，禁止他們使用尚未開放的 API 。此舉將令 Android 平台上的開發工作變得更加嚴謹。<br />\n<br />\n隨著 Android 系統的預載功能愈來愈多， Google 為保障用戶資料安全及服務品質，採取相關限制亦是無可厚非。"},{"pid":"ddc2b5641bf546e3433df2a5b34e067b43ed7a65","tid":551155,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6214006a9f4d6ab90b23763271b1bd90bab141","tid":551155,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:13:56.000Z","msg":"弱弱一問而家係咪已經冇左..."}]}